#   - Paddle.js (결제): cdn.paddle.com / *.paddle.com
#   - Google OAuth: accounts.google.com / apis.google.com / oauth2.googleapis.com / www.googleapis.com
#   - Vimeo (영상): player.vimeo.com / vimeo.com
#   - Placeholder 이미지: placehold.co
#   - 자체 API: api.amazingkorean.net

